"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928003-team-gb-olympic-games-charlotte-dujardin\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Charlotte Dujardin has cast a dark shadow over not just herself but the whole of Team GB heading into the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9973661266853964, \"rank\": 0.0026400642730964098, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer was meant to be a historic moment where women's sport was thrust into the spotlight as we celebrated our nation's greatest female Olympian of all time.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998559797053, \"rank\": 1.4379143484189295e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin is tied with Laura Kenny on six medals and was a dead cert to add to her collection.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the dressage star has been suspended for disgustingly whipping a horse in the legs 24 times in one minute.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This wasn't a racing whip either, it was a long lunge whip that makes a nasty noise when connecting with the victim.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not uncommon for lunge whips to be used in dressage training.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is meant to encourage a horse to eloquently trot.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not meant to distress the horse so much that it cowers towards the wall, jumping every couple of seconds to escape the incoming blows.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no way Dujardin can be allowed to compete again if this is the way she treats the animals.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The three governing bodies who have launched investigations must be thorough to see if this \\\"error of judgment\\\" has happened before.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if they are a few years late.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Consequently, instead of building excitement for Team GB's medal hopefuls, we are discussing an act of cruelty that should never be seen again.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9973661266853964, \"rank\": 0.0026400642730964098, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ratcliffe apology  CAN somebody check on Paula Ratcliffe after she wished convicted child rapist Steven van de Velde \\\"good luck\\\" at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1347, \"